cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of adversarial examples in deep learning, which is a common topic in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed method involves training a deep network to better distinguish adversarial examples from normal ones, which is a task related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
